      61.55,
      505.59,
      102.45
    ],
    "text": "Investigations have been initiated by Marawila Police following a report of a fatal assault involving a sharp weapon in the Nattandiya town area within the Marawila Police Division during the early hours of 06.06.2026.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
