  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      111.61,
      512.24,
      193.89
    ],
    "text": "On the night of 06.06.2026, officers of the Ambalangoda Police Station, assisted by the Ambalangoda Police Special Task Force, conducted a raid on a Facebook-organized party in the Ponaduwa area within the Ambalangoda Police Division. During the operation, 25 individuals and 3 suspects were arrested, along with the seizure of 225 milligrams of cocaine, 8 milligrams of crystal methamphetamine (\u201cice\u201d), 2 milligrams of cannabis, and 400 milligrams of illegal cigarettes.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      208.45,
      516.42,
      249.36
    ],
    "text": "The arrested individuals, aged between 18 and 44 years, are residents of Batapola, Uragasmanhandiya, Balapitiya, Homagama, Beruwala, Ambalangoda, Meetiyagoda, Wathugedara, and Ahungalla areas.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      263.92,
      454.06,
      277.2
    ],
    "text": "Further investigations are being conducted by the Ambalangoda Police.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
